@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_epgdeh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (0.26 - wp.sin(0.11))
    v1 = tmp
    v2 = (v2 - 0.01)
    v0 = 0.76
    v2 = 0.13
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.sin((tmp + 0.63 - v2 + 0.39)))
    tmp = wp.cos((wp.abs(v0 + 0.93) + v1))
    data[tid] = v0
